---
import img1 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/render2.png';
import img2 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/render3.png';
import img3 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/render5.png';
import img4 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/render6.png';
import img5 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/drum1.png';
import img7 from '../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/drum2.png';
import LearnBtn from '../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro';
import videoProv from "../../assets/images/DrumMixers/PlaC140ET.mp4";
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-10 md:mt-20 text-white">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 justify-center items-start gap-4">
            <div class="hidden justify-end items-end md:flex h-full">
                <Image src={img5} alt="" class="w-[100%]"/>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex-col items-start justify-start pt-4 md:flex">
                <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl text-black text-center w-full">Two Year Warranty</h1>
                <br>
                <p class="md:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT text-center w-full">We stand behind our top-tier quality with the <br>
                highest warranty in the market</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-4 bg-blueMain md:rounded-t-2xl p-8 md:h-full">
                <div class="text-xl md:text-4xl w-full text-start">
                    <h1 class="text-redBg">TRIASO® </h1>
                    <h1 class="">DRUM MIXER</h1>
                </div>
                <p class="text-grisSubP text-base md:text-lg text-justify">
                    High-quality drum mixers designed for durability and efficient asphalt blending. 
                    Featuring heat-resistant alloy steel drums and low air velocity systems, they ensure 
                    energy efficiency, minimal fine loss, and reduced maintenance, all while delivering 
                    consistent and reliable results in demanding conditions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full bg-blueMain p-6">
            <h1 class="text-xl md:text-4xl">RANGING FROM 10 TO 500 TPH</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="block md:hidden">
            <Image src={img7} alt="" class="w-1/2"/>
            <div class="flex-col flex md:hidden items-start justify-start pt-4">
                <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl text-black text-center w-full">Two Year Warranty</h1>
                <br>
                <p class="md:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT text-center w-full">We stand behind our top-tier quality with the <br>
                highest warranty in the market</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 text-black px-8 lg:px-52">
        <h1 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-center md:mb-10">Asphalt plants for the smallest jobs to large projects</h1>
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-center text-grisT">Discover all asphalt plants ranges and models ></h2>
        <h1>AQUI VA UN VIDEO</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 text-black lg:px-52">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-start mb-5 w-full px-8">
            Integral 10 Tph <br> Asphalt Plants
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-start w-full px-8">Ideal for municipal jobs and road maintenance</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-blueMain text-base md:text-xl px-8">
            Reduces production costs for small-volume asphalt manufacturing by optimizing startups, 
            minimizing fuel consumption, and lowering labor and transportation expenses.
        </p>
        <Image src={img1} alt=""/>
        <h1 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blueMain px-8">Learn more of our <span class="text-redBg">incredible</span> 10 Tph Asphalt Plants ></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 px-8 md:px-52 w-full">
        <h1>AQUI VIDEO 1</h1>
        <h1>AQUI VIDEO 2</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="md:mx-52 mx-8 p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Retractable Elevator for Efficient Transport and Operation
            </h2>
        <div class="">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
                <video src={videoProv} autoplay muted playsinline class="w-3/5"></video>
            </div>
            <p class="text-grisT text-justify">
                Triaso’s vertical elevator is designed with a retractable configuration that complies 
                with DOT transportation height limits, ensuring safe and legal road transport. 
                Once the drum mixer is installed on-site, the elevator extends to its full operational height,
                 allowing for efficient material transfer with minimal setup time. 
                 This smart design improves logistics while maintaining high performance during loading and 
                 discharge.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 px-8 lg:px-52">
        <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center gap-8 mt-20 mb-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center gap-4">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-redBg">Hot-mix</h1>
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-4">Pugmill</h1>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisP text-justify">
                    The pugmill is an essential component at the end of the drum mix process,
                     where the hot mix is finalized to ensure a homogeneous and high-quality blend. This 
                     is achieved through two robust shafts equipped with flights that thoroughly mix the material,
                      providing consistency and uniformity.
                </p>
                <Image src={img2} alt="" class="block md:hidden my-4"/>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisP text-justify">
                    Its durable construction ensures smooth operation
                       and long-term reliability, while its efficient mixing mechanism allows precise control 
                       over the final mix. Designed for easy maintenance and operation, the pugmill delivers consistent
                        performance in demanding industrial environments.
                </p>
            </div>
            <Image src={img2} alt="" class="hidden md:block"/>
        </div>
        <LearnBtn />

    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 px-8 md:px-52">
        <h1 class="lg:text-4xl text-2xl text-grisT w-full text-end mb-10">CONTROL SYSTEM</h1>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-10"> 
            <Image src={img4} alt="Control System" class="rounded-2xl order-2 lg:order-1"/>
            <p class="lg:text-lg text-base text-grisT text-justify order-1 lg:order-2">At Triaso, we don’t believe in standardized solutions—especially when it comes to our 
                control systems. We recognize that each client operates under unique conditions, with 
                specific priorities in automation, data handling, usability, and investment. 
                That’s why every control cabin we build is tailored to fit those distinct requirements.
                 From interface design to functional integration,
                 we carefully configure each system to match the operational goals and workflow of 
                 every customer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10"> 
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl text-sm lg:text-base flex flex-col text-start justify-center p-4">
                    <h1 class="text-black mb-4">Visualization and control of materials consumption (current and cumulative).</h1>
                    <p class="text-grisT font-normal">Enables real-time monitoring of 
                        material usage, while tracking total consumption over time for accurate
                         records and optimized production.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <ol class="list-disc font-normal text-sm lg:text-base text-grisT ml-8">
                        <li>Asphalt</li>
                        <li>Aggregates</li>
                        <li>Fuel Consumption</li>
                        <li>Water Usage</li>
                        <li>Recycled Asphalt Pavement (RAP)</li>
                        <li>Additives</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl text-sm lg:text-base flex flex-col text-start justify-center p-4 text-grisT">
                    <h2>Customizable production management with storage for thousands of recipes.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm lg:text-base flex text-start justify-center p-4 gap-10 text-grisT">
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-black lg:text-2xl text-xl">Versatile Setup</h1>
                        <p>Works seamlessly in a dedicated control cabin or 
                            under a protective roof.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-black lg:text-2xl text-xl">Quick Adjustments</h1>
                        <p>Allows rapid changes to recipes or control 
                            settings to match project requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 text-grisT">
                
                <p class="lg:text-lg text-base text-justify">Offering a practical and efficient way to achieve total control over your asphalt
                     plant operations. With advanced monitoring and automation, it simplifies the
                      management of key processes such as temperature control, material dosing, and production 
                      rates. Designed to adapt to different setups, it ensures reliable performance 
                      while prioritizing safety and ease of use.</p>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl text-sm lg:text-base flex flex-col text-start justify-center p-4 text-grisT">
                    <h2>Walls and roof made of 16-gauge sheet metal with insulated panels.</h2>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal">Provides durability and thermal insulation, ensuring structural 
                        strength while maintaining a controlled interior environment.</p>
                        <br>
                    <ol class="list-disc ml-8">
                        <li>Built with reinforced materials for heavy-duty use.</li>
                        <li>Panoramic windows for enhanced visibility.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 px-8 md:px-52 font-bold">
        <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl mb-4">User-Friendly Interface</h1>
        <h2 class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT mb-4 font-normal md:mb-20">Simplifies configuration adjustments for operators with minimal downtime.</h2>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-grisT mb-4 md:mb-16 text-justify">Created to offer plant operators a deeper understanding of their operation,
             this cloud-based platform stores all production data remotely and securely.
              It gives you the freedom to access detailed performance analytics from any 
              location and any device—whether you're in the office, on the road, or at a job 
              site. With real-time access to trends, logs, and operational metrics, decision-making
               becomes faster, more informed, and fully independent of your physical location.
        </p>
        <button class="bg-redBg rounded-full 
        font-normal max-w-[200px] text-white py-1 px-4 
        text-sm md:text-lg hover:bg-redBgHover" aria-label="Let´s get started">Let´s Get Started</button>
    </div>
</div>